Let $p_s$ be the probability that a step remains on a high-priority edge. The mass trapped is:
$$\frac{\alpha}{1 - p_s(1-\alpha)} \ge 0.75 \implies p_s \ge \frac{1 - \frac{4}{3}\alpha}{1-\alpha} \equiv K_\alpha$$

